attributes.Long form description: The student is disassembling a rolling cart. He takes the top tray off and puts the pieces on the table. Then unscrews the hex nuts from the middle and bottom trays and withdraws the brackets. Then disassembles the right and left legs. Then flips the bar frame and unscrews the wheels from the rolling cart. Finally, He disassembles the base frame of the rolling cart.
